that such acts will force us to compromise or capitulate, they are
wrong and will always be wrong.
   We are the true Islamic nation of Mohammed, in whose flesh and
blood martyrdom has been mixed since Al-Hussein's Ashoura. We are
the nation of glorious Jihad (Holy War), in which Islam has bred
the spirit of confidence and insubordination to no one but almight
God.
