spy Col. Higgins' link to the U.S. Central Intelligence Agency has
been proven beyond a shred of doubt. He coordinated conspiratorial
efforts by the CIA and the Zionist enemy to hit at Moslem forces
and their struggle against Israel.
   We have announced that in a previous statement and emphasized
that he has been admitted into the circle of serious danger after
the death sentence that had been handed down against him.
Therefore, we reiterate today that we shall carry out by hanging
the death sentence handed down against proven spy Higgins at
exactly 3 p.m. (8 a.m. EDT) Monday if Sheik Abdul Karim Obeid and
his two brethren have not been freed by then.
   This will be our first response to the stupid Israeli aggression
and the flagrant American support that proves U.S. complicity in
the crime. Procrastination will be futile and so will be repentance
afterward.
   The Organization of the Oppressed on Earth.
